-- Russia’s Foreign Minister Discusses Iran, Syria With EU Official
-- B y   K s e n i a   G a l o u c h k o
-- 2012-06-03T16:16:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-03/russia-s-foreign-minister-discusses-iran-syria-with-eu-official.html
Russian Foreign Affairs Minister
 Sergei Lavrov  met with European Union foreign policy chief
Catherine Ashton to discuss the Iranian nuclear program and
Syria, according to a statement on the Russian ministry’s
website today.  The officials met before the start of a two-day bilateral
summit in St. Petersburg.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ksenia Galouchko in Moscow at 
 kgalouchko1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  